  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.1,
      "size": 17568,
      "text": "欢迎来到马尔可夫链实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "你有没有想过，天气预报是如何预测明天的天气？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "或者搜索引擎是如何给网页排名的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "这些问题都可以用马尔可夫链来建模和解决。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "马尔可夫链是一种随机过程，下一个状态只依赖于当前状态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "这个性质叫做无记忆性：过去的历史不影响未来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "状态之间的转移概率可以用一个矩阵来表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "让我们通过一个简单的例子来理解这个概念。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "transition",
      "line_id": "trans-1",
      "filename": "transition-trans-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/transition-trans-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.44,
      "size": 23040,
      "text": "假设天气只有晴天和雨天两种状态。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "transition",
      "line_id": "trans-2",
      "filename": "transition-trans-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/transition-trans-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.99,
      "size": 47808,
      "text": "如果今天是晴天，明天有70%的概率还是晴天，30%的概率变成雨天。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "transition",
      "line_id": "trans-3",
      "filename": "transition-trans-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/transition-trans-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.97,
      "size": 47520,
      "text": "如果今天是雨天，明天有40%的概率变成晴天，60%的概率还是雨天。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "transition",
      "line_id": "trans-4",
      "filename": "transition-trans-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/transition-trans-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "这些概率构成了转移矩阵，决定了系统的长期行为。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "steady-state",
      "line_id": "steady-1",
      "filename": "steady-state-steady-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/steady-state-steady-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "经过足够长的时间，马尔可夫链会趋向一个稳态分布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "steady-state",
      "line_id": "steady-2",
      "filename": "steady-state-steady-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/steady-state-steady-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "在稳态下，各状态的概率不再随时间变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "steady-state",
      "line_id": "steady-3",
      "filename": "steady-state-steady-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/steady-state-steady-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "稳态分布是转移矩阵的特征向量，对应特征值1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "steady-state",
      "line_id": "steady-4",
      "filename": "steady-state-steady-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/steady-state-steady-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "这个性质使得马尔可夫链成为分析长期行为的有力工具。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23760,
      "text": "马尔可夫链在许多领域都有重要应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.53,
      "size": 24480,
      "text": "Google的PageRank算法就是基于马尔可夫链。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/markov-chain/xiaoxiao/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "语音识别和自然语言处理大量使用隐马尔可夫模型。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "markov-chain",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
